\"_blank\">https://t.me/ncetransport/18725</a>"},{"pid":"01ff22101c4da65dcc7a845421d1f4bac1b72e1e","tid":1867530,"uid":19711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"撐醫護呀dllm !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813e9fddaede6d4a5d5971c04341a18a97ff3645","tid":1867530,"uid":301067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"720146e8a47d5c8a4778809ae20e5ad7c50b18be","tid":1867530,"uid":201826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}